The air dryer, which blows air from the unit at speeds, is said to be 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), managed to blow the micro-organisms of the hands and the unit and potentially contaminate other users of the bathroom and the bathroom environment at a distance of up to 2 metres.
